data.title: The Chantoozies
data.meta_description:
We sat down with the epic Ally Fowler and Eve von Bibra of the  @thechantoozies6568 
We had a blast from the past, and a look into the future. We chatted about the difficulties of getting your music heard, but in typical 'The Chantoozies" style, we had fun, and at the end of the day thats what it is all about!
